title: The Best From Week 1
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho, and Rod Gilmore looks back at the top games of week one. Plus, Florida State's head coach Mike Norvell joins the show after the Seminoles crazy win, Also, the crew previews as Alabama makes their way to Texas on Saturday.
